Class HtmlFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • SystemSolaire.HtmlFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class HtmlFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    HtmlFile is a Java Class which have four attributes who specialize a Html File (Location , baliseTitle , baliseH1 , last-modification) -(baliseTitle,baliseH1) is tags : a basic element of HTML Files -Html File is used to describe the visual appearance and the content of a WEB page -the most known tags are (html,head,body,title,h1..) -so this class can recover the principal tags of an (this class instance) with two specialized method(findH1(),findTitle)
    Since:
    JDK8.0
    Version:
    1.8.0_144 created at 15 Dec,2017
    Author:
    Ayad Ishak and Arhab Samira
